        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your body excretes abrasive chemicals in your slime when you're threatened. When you use @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.ancestry-features.Item.Slime Squirt] or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Slime Spray], creatures in the area take @Damage[floor(@item.level/3)d4[persistent,acid]] damage with a basic @Check[reflex|against:class-spell] saving throw against the higher of your class DC or spell DC. At 12th level and every three levels thereafter, the persistent acid damage increases by 1d4.</p>"
